    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一款古埃及城市建造游戏，主要考验生存、扩张和创造能力。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在尼罗河畔的流沙之中，初生的文明需要英明的领袖来引领它走向辉煌。传承法老的衣钵，创造一座繁荣的城市，发现资源，面对洪水、饥荒和喜怒无常的诸神，生存并发展下去。你会为子民创造一片乐土吗？你会安抚诸神还是成为诸神之一？还是消逝在漫漫黄沙之中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/808ca8227ba06ac447141e7fad4b7305.poster.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/808ca8227ba06ac447141e7fad4b7305.webm?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/808ca8227ba06ac447141e7fad4b7305.mp4?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《沙漠王朝》采用了创新的模拟型游戏方式，玩家要与季节、昼夜循环、天气、野生动物和疾病作斗争，细节满满，以至于要考虑到每个村民的个人欲望、希望和梦想。在玩家平衡利用诸神之力，开发城市并持续增长人口的过程中，要克服这些系统和环境带来的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《沙漠王朝》的游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富而深入的城市建造工具，让玩家可以充分表达自我，展现他们对梦幻古埃及的愿景 - 在山坡上建造楼梯、在水面上建造桥梁、在高墙上塑造雄伟雕像等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村民事件系统以一种新颖的形式呈现了创造性城市建造目标。个别村民会提出独特要求，需要在建造城市时给出解决方案。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度模拟，拥有昼夜、天气、野生动物、疾病以及其他诸多系统，玩家将置身于这个不断变化的的世界，享受充满变数和引人入胜的游戏体验。在玩家开发城市以维持人口不断增长时，需要克服这些系统带来的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入奇幻元素，远古人民心目中的诸神将真实存在。玩家需要满足或拒绝诸神不断提出的要求，或者通过自己的努力成为诸神之一。每一个选择都会产生持久的影响。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/ed35ab212b348f6b174ce5dacc45da88.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白手起家，探索并利用土地、河流和野生动物，开创你的文明。与季节、饥渴、疾病、危险的野生动物等作斗争，克服古代生活要面临的危险。建立资源链，为子民提供必需品。学会在恶劣的沙漠条件下管理城市。应对压力，安抚好诸神，否则就要承担可能的后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4dff56f490d617216cdfc8af57309c4e.poster.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4dff56f490d617216cdfc8af57309c4e.webm?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4dff56f490d617216cdfc8af57309c4e.mp4?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/8a319eaaad55fbf0bc5adffa647b42f4.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用强大的建造工具，将你子民的居住地从简陋的泥屋村落升级成沙漠中的宏伟城市。利用丰富的创造性选项，以自己喜欢的方式建造城市（建筑、装饰、植物、水道、平台、道路、楼梯）。制定法律和命令，让城市自行有序运转，而你则得以将精力集中在帝国最重要的方面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4a75bb32a80e1e3a2c91fdf9ce6addd8.poster.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4a75bb32a80e1e3a2c91fdf9ce6addd8.webm?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/4a75bb32a80e1e3a2c91fdf9ce6addd8.mp4?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/e0fc98a4b2c290dc9b52ef506061bcf6.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地图，发现有趣事物、资源储量和各种</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >草木鸟兽。利用新发现的知识研究技术，从而建造新建筑并升级建筑，扩大自己的地盘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/a707e9101fb75b34f78aff1e5cd0ace7.poster.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/a707e9101fb75b34f78aff1e5cd0ace7.webm?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/a707e9101fb75b34f78aff1e5cd0ace7.mp4?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/3594f5b95f035c9e1a2e83fae993db22.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《沙漠王朝》倾力呈现可以无限游玩的乐趣。完成其中一个最终目标只意味着游戏主剧情的结束，但达成最终目标后，玩家仍然可以继续扩张，考验自己的基础设施建设能力，以满足不断增长的人口。无限游玩让玩家有机会为自己的理想而奋斗，在曾经是不毛之地的沙漠中创造一个真正的天堂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/bf5948387f46fa642cd21ed235b5dbd4.poster.avif?t=1758722900\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/bf5948387f46fa642cd21ed235b5dbd4.webm?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1143070/extras/bf5948387f46fa642cd21ed235b5dbd4.mp4?t=1758722900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
